<head>THEN</head>
    <list type="translations">
        <item xml:lang="zh">那時</item>
    </list>
<div type="definition">
<p>ASSUMING FOR ARGUMENT that the PRECEDING SENTENCE IS TRUE. Contrast THEREUPON.</p>
    <div type="definition" resp="#CH" modified="2023-09-13T01:48:02.494+09:00">
